#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. HTML: </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:0.3"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍa"
msgstr "Monks’ Undetermined"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:0.4"
msgid "2. Dutiyaaniyatasikkhāpada"
msgstr "2. The second training rule"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-vp-en1.336, pts-cs-bu-an2.1, ms1V_1829 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī—“bhagavatā paṭikkhittaṃ mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappetun”ti tassāyeva kumārikāya saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappesi kālayuttaṃ samullapanto kālayuttaṃ dhammaṃ bhaṇanto."
msgstr "At this time Venerable Udāyī knew that the Master had prohibited sitting alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable for doing it, and so instead he sat alone in private with the same girl. When they were able, they just chatted; otherwise he gave her a teaching."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.3"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho visākhā migāramātā nimantitā taṃ kulaṃ agamāsi."
msgstr "A second time Visākhā had been invited to that family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.4"
msgid "Addasā kho visākhā migāramātā āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ tassāyeva kumārikāya saddhiṃ ekaṃ ekāya raho nisinnaṃ."
msgstr "When she arrived, she saw Udāyī sitting alone in private with the same girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.5"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and she said to Udāyī,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.6"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ yaṃ ayyo mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappeti."
msgstr "“Venerable, it’s not appropriate that you should sit alone with a woman on a private seat."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.7"
msgid "Kiñcāpi, bhante, ayyo anatthiko tena dhammena, api ca dussaddhāpayā appasannā manussā”ti."
msgstr "Although you may not be aiming at that act, people with little confidence are hard to convince.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.8"
msgid "Evampi kho āyasmā udāyī visākhāya migāramātuyā vuccamāno nādiyi."
msgstr "But Udāyī did not listen."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.9"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nikkhamitvā bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "After leaving, Visākhā told the monks about what had happened."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.10"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.11"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.12"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā udāyī mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappessatī”ti."
msgstr "“How can Venerable Udāyī sit alone with a woman on a private seat?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2, ms1V_1830 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.13"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After rebuking Udāyī in many ways, they told the Master …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.14"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, udāyi, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappesī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, Udāyī, that you sat alone with a woman on a private seat?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.15"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.16"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.17"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappessasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit alone with a woman on a private seat?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.18"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.19"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.19a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc3, pts-vp-pli3.192, ms1V_1831
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.20"
msgid "“Na heva kho pana paṭicchannaṃ āsanaṃ hoti nālaṅkammaniyaṃ, alañca kho hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsituṃ."
msgstr "‘Although a seat is not concealed, nor suitable for doing it, it may be suitable for speaking lewdly to a woman."

#. REF: pts-vp-en1.337
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.21"
msgid "Yo pana bhikkhu tathārūpe āsane mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisajjaṃ kappeyya, tamenaṃ saddheyyavacasā upāsikā disvā dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya—"
msgstr "If a monk sits alone with a woman in private on such a seat, and a trustworthy female lay follower sees him and accuses him of"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.22"
msgid "saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing confession,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.23"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno dvinnaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "then, if he admits to the sitting, he is be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.24"
msgid "saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "according to one of these two"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.25"
msgid "Yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr "or according to what that trustworthy female lay follower has said."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:1.26"
msgid "Ayampi dhammo aniyato”ti."
msgstr "This rule too is undetermined.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc4, pts-cs-bu-an2.2.1, ms1V_1832
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.1"
msgid "Na heva kho pana paṭicchannaṃ āsanaṃ hotīti"
msgstr "Although a seat is not concealed:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.2"
msgid "appaṭicchannaṃ hoti kuṭṭena vā kavāṭena vā kilañjena vā sāṇipākārena vā rukkhena vā thambhena vā kotthaḷiyā vā yena kenaci appaṭicchannaṃ hoti."
msgstr "it is not concealed by a wall, a screen, a door, a screening cloth, a tree, a pillar, a grain container, or anything else."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc5, ms1V_1833
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.3"
msgid "Nālaṅkammaniyanti"
msgstr "Nor suitable for doing it:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.4"
msgid "na sakkā hoti methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevituṃ."
msgstr "one is not able to have sexual intercourse."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc6, ms1V_1834
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.5"
msgid "Alañca kho hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsitunti"
msgstr "It may be suitable for speaking lewdly to a woman:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.1.6"
msgid "sakkā hoti mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsituṃ."
