msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.34"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho nipanno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but lying down,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.35"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.36"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho ṭhito”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.37"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc21, pts-vp-en1.339, ms1V_1849 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.38"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.39"
msgid "“ayyassa mayā sutaṃ nipannassa mātugāmaṃ duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsantassā”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve heard you speaking lewdly to a woman while lying down,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.40"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the offense. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.41"
msgid "saccāhaṃ nipanno, no ca kho duṭṭhullāhi vācāhi obhāsinti,"
msgstr "“It’s true that I was lying down, but I didn’t speak lewdly,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.42"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.43"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho nisinno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but seated,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.44"
msgid "nisajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the sitting. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.45"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho ṭhito”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.46"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc22, ms1V_1850 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.47"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.48"
msgid "“ayyo mayā diṭṭho mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nisinno”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you seated alone with a woman in private,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.49"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, nisajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the sitting. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.50"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho nipanno”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but lying down,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.51"
msgid "nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.52"
msgid "“nāhaṃ nisinno, api ca kho ṭhito”ti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t seated, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.53"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc23, ms1V_1851 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.54"
msgid "Sā ce evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If she accuses him thus:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.55"
msgid "“ayyo mayā diṭṭho mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho nipanno”ti,"
msgstr "“I’ve seen you lying down alone with a woman in private,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.56"
msgid "so ca taṃ paṭijānāti, nipajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "and he admits to that, then he is to be dealt with for the lying down. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.57"
msgid "nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho nisinnoti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but seated,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.58"
msgid "nisajjāya kāretabbo … pe …"
msgstr "then he is to be dealt with for the sitting. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.59"
msgid "nāhaṃ nipanno, api ca kho ṭhitoti,"
msgstr "“I wasn’t lying down, but standing,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.60"
msgid "na kāretabbo."
msgstr "then he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p></div><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc24, ms1V_1852
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.61"
msgid "Ayampīti"
msgstr "This rule too:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.62"
msgid "purimaṃ upādāya vuccati."
msgstr "this is said with reference to the previous undetermined rule."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="term"> 
#. REF: sc25, ms1V_1853
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.63"
msgid "Aniyatoti"
msgstr "Undetermined:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.64"
msgid "na niyato,"
msgstr "not determined."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:2.2.65"
msgid "saṃghādiseso vā pācittiyaṃ vā."
msgstr "It is either an offense entailing suspension or an offense entailing confession."

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc26, pts-cs-bu-an2.3, ms1V_1854 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.1"
msgid "Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he admits to going, and he admits to sitting, and he admits to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.2"
msgid "Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he admits to going, but he does not admit to sitting, yet he admits to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.3"
msgid "Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, nisajjāya kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he admits to going, and he admits to sitting, but he does not admit to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the sitting."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.4"
msgid "Gamanaṃ paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, na kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he admits to going, but he does not admit to sitting, nor does he admit to an offense, he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc27, ms1V_1855 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.5"
msgid "Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he does not admit to going, but he admits to sitting, and he admits to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.6"
msgid "Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ paṭijānāti, āpattiyā kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he does not admit to going, nor does he admit to sitting, but he admits to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the offense."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.7"
msgid "Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, nisajjāya kāretabbo."
msgstr "If he does not admit to going, but he admits to sitting, yet he does not admit to an offense, he is to be dealt with for the sitting."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.8"
msgid "Gamanaṃ na paṭijānāti nisajjaṃ na paṭijānāti āpattiṃ na paṭijānāti, na kāretabboti."
msgstr "If he does not admit to going, nor does he admit to sitting, nor does he admit to an offense, he is not to be dealt with."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc28, ms1V_1856 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.9"
msgid "Dutiyo aniyato niṭṭhito."
msgstr "The second undetermined rule is finished."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc29, pts-vp-pli3.194, pts-vp-en1.340, ms1V_1857 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.10"
msgid "Uddiṭṭhā kho āyasmanto dve aniyatā dhammā."
msgstr "“Venerables, the two undetermined rules have been recited."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.11"
msgid "Tatthāyasmante pucchāmi—"
msgstr "In regard to this I ask you,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.12"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.13"
msgid "Dutiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A second time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.14"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.15"
msgid "Tatiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.16"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.17"
msgid "Parisuddhetthāyasmanto;"
msgstr "You are pure in this"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.18"
msgid "tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "and therefore silent."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.19"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmīti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.”"

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection summary">
#. REF: sc30, ms1V_1858 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.20"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ"
msgstr "This is the summary:"

#. HTML: </p><div class="uddana"><p>
#. REF: sc31, ms1V_1859 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.21"
msgid "Alaṃ kammaniyañceva,"
msgstr "Suitable for doing it,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.22"
msgid "tatheva ca naheva kho;"
msgstr "And then not so;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.23"
msgid "Aniyatā supaññattā,"
msgstr "The undetermined rules have been well laid down"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.24"
msgid "buddhaseṭṭhena tādināti."
msgstr "By the Stable One, the Buddha who is the best."

#. HTML: </p></div><p class="endsection">
#. REF: sc32, ms1V_1860 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay2:3.25"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The chapter on undetermined rules is finished."
